reviewText: Kiersten found this DVD in her Easter basket and was very happy about it.She already had Springtime For Max And Ruby and really enjoys watching it.She likes Party Time With Max And Ruby equally well.There are 12 episodes each about 8 minutes long.Sadly,Max and Ruby is no longer shown on Nick,so if your child/grandchild liked Max and Ruby,having a DVD or two of this show is worth the cost.
